===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# {{lb|en|Christianity}} A religious movement which believes that only the spiritual 'law of Faith' (Romans 3:27) is essential for salvation; and which is 'against' all other practical 'laws' being taught as being essential for salvation; and referring to them as [[legalism]].
# {{lb|en|Judaism}} Opposition to the [[Torah]].

